Class Stack<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.nsu.cjvth.stack.Stack<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Type of elements
    public class Stack<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Stack of any non-primitive type. You can add and get one or multiple elements at once.
